author: dreid
msg: The Atom specification specifies Atom:feed as being correct and contrary to
my previous thoughts, we have only one DOAP within Atom feed - which uses the
correct 'feed' and presently we are ignoring it! This change brings us inline
with the spec and allows us to parse the existing DOAP within Atom file.
